data.description: Better than new!  This home is barely lived in with some upgrades everyone wants! New privacy wood fence with solar lighting!  New Large 20 x 24 Concrete Patio Slab! New 8 x 12 x 8  Custom Built Wood Storage Shed! Cozy Firepit area! The Dupont Plan offers 4 Bedrooms and 3 Full Baths.  Guest Bed & Bath on Main Level.  Open Floor plan! Granite countertops with huge island in kitchen!  Perfect for food prep, baking and entertaining!  Dining area with glass double doors overlooking the beautiful backyard.   Upstairs you will enjoy the loft area!  Game room, TV, office, craft, reading area, anything you want it to be!  Master suite is spacious and has a nice en suite bath.  Huge walk in shower, double vanity with granite top. Large laundry room upstairs!   2 more generous secondary bedrooms upstairs with a full bath that also has a granite counter top. The garage is newly painted and is ready for your big screen TV!   This home is so nice!  Owner job transfer.   Upgrades done to the house: Concrete Patio Expansion:  $3700 Fence:  $9800 Custom Built Wood Shed:  $11000 Sod:  $3000 Blinds, ceiling fans, electrical & paint:  $1800 Firepit:  $1700 Landscaping:  $850 Convenient location to 19/41 and easy access to I-75. Very desirable area!
